node.text:
The World's Frist Vape with Safty Fast Charing - Obelisk 120FC release Now!!
---
Directly charge a 3700mAh vape in 15 minutes with USB-C cable, astonishingly fast and assuredly safe.
Ultra-long battery life keeps up for 2 days and allows to share your power with loved ones.
Co-worked perfectly with leakproof Geekvape Z Sub-ohm Tank or Obelisk Tank with childproof safety design,
Obelisk 120 FC awaits you to explore.
.
.
.
.
.
.
Warning: You must be of legal age to vape, thank you.
